[48;2;42;45;68m  ### What was done?                                                                                                                                      [49m
[48;2;42;45;68m                                                                                                                                                          [49m
[48;2;42;45;68m  1. **Removed Redundancy:** Consolidated the duplicate Python API quickstart snippets into a single, cohesive, and logical flow.                         [49m
