[48;2;42;45;68m  ## 📊 Diagnostics & Latent Space Auditing                                                                                                               [49m
[48;2;42;45;68m                                                                                                                                                          [49m
[48;2;42;45;68m  `sajepa` avoids representation collapse natively by evaluating the effective rank and spatial variance of the predictor. You can track model health     [49m
[48;2;42;45;68m  across sessions using the built-in diagnostic suite:                                                                                                    [49m
[48;2;42;45;68m                                                                                                                                                          [49m
[48;2;42;45;68m  ```bash                                                                                                                                                 [49m
