[48;2;42;45;68m                                                                                                                                                          [49m
[48;2;42;45;68m  # Train using an explicit configuration configuration                                                                                                   [49m
[48;2;42;45;68m  sajepa-train --config configs/examples/mhd_2d_ms1p2.json --sessions-dir sessions                                                                        [49m
